  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3, W-EP-04)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level is 3. Thirteen credibility factors are scaffolded; ten are assessed with full gradation data, while three factors — Numerical solver error, Use error, and Equivalency of input parameters — are marked not-assessed on the basis that they were considered beyond the current project scope. No concrete justification is provided for why these factors fall outside scope at MRL 3, leaving a material epistemic gap consistent with W-EP-04.",
