    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/cou2-vad-mrl3-accepted",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the CFD hemolysis model for the VAD COU at MRL 3 based on the ten assessed factors, noting that seven of ten assessed factors achieved at least Gradation 2 and three achieved the required Gradation 3. Three factors — Numerical solver error, Use error, and Equivalency of input parameters — were not assessed and were characterized as beyond scope for the current phase. The team concluded that the assessed evidence was sufficient to support a Low assurance level acceptance, deferring the unassessed factors to future work without quantifying the credibility gap they introduce.",
